data.description: Warm and spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom mobile home nestled on a sprawling 1.6-acre lot in the serene countryside near Jennings. Located within the sought-after Hathaway school district, this residence boasts 2 generous living areas and a large open kitchen with an inviting island at its heart. Retreat to the master bathroom, complete with a luxurious soaker tub and a separate shower for a spa-like experience. Outside, the property features a large carport suitable for both parking and entertaining, making it the perfect space for gatherings with friends and family. Welcome to your new retreat where modern comfort meets the tranquility of rural living.
